{"tid":310798,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Tree gun後生廿年靠水光槍　皮膚科醫生：美容效果成疑","createTime":"2017-07-06T06:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T06:08:38.000Z","uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd52f5608db542ad5491c345adf8c525691a6451","tid":310798,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170706/org/1499268587_8496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170706%2Forg%2F1499268587_8496.jpg&h=ccac0115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/07/05/3386195/20170706_sub738newAD_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F3386195%2F20170706_sub738newAD_clean_w.mp4&d=mXW1LrfLg36pVxJ5GqLHJ0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=74c749eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/07/05/3386195/20170706_sub738newAD_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170706/large/sub73801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170706%2Flarge%2Fsub73801.jpg&h=6d34406c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 最近樹根上載三張做treatment的相片到facebook，分享水光槍如何該他回復青春。（鍾樹根facebook圖片） <br />\n <br />\n樹根不做議員疑似轉行做美容KOL，最近他上載了三張做treatment的相片到facebook，加上一堆KOL賣廣告式的Hashtag，說打完水光槍回復青春兼後生廿年，真是樹根都變樹苗。不過看他的樣子&hellip;&hellip;敷麻醉膏還用保鮮紙包臉，信唔信得過？ <br />\n <br />\n水光槍又名水光針，是一種用電腦注入美顏物質的注射方法。皮膚科醫生史泰祖指：「水光槍一般是注射物質進入皮膚，普遍有化學物質、維他命，用作美容用途，把藥物或化學物質打進皮膚來融化脂肪，多年來在融化脂肪和改善皮膚方面的效果成疑，普遍來說不被所有醫學界接受。」水光槍不同於傳統的透明質酸注射，透明質酸需用人手在不同部位注射，而水光槍則是在不同部位注入微小的劑量，注射後會有輕微出血的現象，醫生亦不建議全面注射。再看他打的四字hashtag，由英語界轉戰美容界都不忘造字。當中的「FGF」原來是一些聲稱可令肌膚再生的物質，難道樹根想逆齡變小鮮肉？ <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170706/large/sub73802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170706%2Flarge%2Fsub73802.jpg&h=e3bb478f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 敷麻醉膏還用保鮮紙包臉，信唔信得過？（鍾樹根facebook圖片） <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170706/large/sub73803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170706%2Flarge%2Fsub73803.jpg&h=2f114711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 十足美容KOL分享美容後效果圖。（鍾樹根facebook圖片） <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170706/large/sub73804.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170706%2Flarge%2Fsub73804.png&h=58494616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 去年消委會指部份針劑的安全性成疑，有機會引致敏感、感染和留疤痕。（消委會圖片） <br />\n <br />\n網民還關心樹根是不是轉行賣廣告，他就不直接回應，用例子答你：「生物科技產品，香港科技大學發明。」醫生就回應指水光槍已有四五十年的歷史，主要先在歐洲流行起來，直至近年才在其他國家出現。雖然不是新美容療程，但至今仍存在風險，去年消委會指出部份針劑的安全性成疑，由於效果只能維持數個月，要經常補打，劑量亦可能需要逐年增加，有機會引致敏感、感染和留疤痕，提醒大家打之前要三思。<br />\n <br />\n記者：黎婉婷"}]}